{"tid":2329445,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"求救 情緒問題 好辛苦","createTime":"2020-12-17T08:44:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-21T07:39:23.000Z","uid":228317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"b23623a7091a2c15f25e1a3cd1fb6ed60674de1e","tid":2329445,"uid":228317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T08:44:12.000Z","msg":"依個禮拜身體好差， <br />\n每日起身好似尋晚冇訓過咁 好攰<br />\n有時候個心跳得好快，呼吸唔暢順 成日抖大氣<br />\n眼皮成日跳 ，又會大力眨眼<br />\n腸胃唔好 多胃氣 屙稀屎<br />\n就算著好多衫都手腳冷 <br />\n個人好緊長 坐立不安 <br />\n<br />\n一個月前因為 耳水不平衡 ，成日諗／驚幾時又發作 好怕嗰種暈既感覺 。之後成日都覺得身體郁下就唔舒服，不停上網睇自己既symptoms. <br />\n<br />\n依排考試 但完全冇精神溫 我計劃下個sem retake 再考 所以冇理過。我嘗試過唔好諗咁多野 試過出街行下 放鬆下 隔咗幾個鐘又係咁 <br />\n<br />\n啱啱屋企人問我做咩冇精神， 我講唔出口，突然之間喊左出黎， 講真我都唔知點解 控制唔到<br />\n<br />\n睇急症？定點？<br />\n<br />\n巴，20歲"},{"pid":"b21a7ea54ab5f2e4d8d71646a9914077b1749371","tid":2329445,"uid":382422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T08:45:07.000Z","msg":"成個禮拜打咗幾多次丁？"},{"pid":"a50f09332fd860ced0505b000194aff0cb9ef20c","tid":2329445,"uid":144198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T13:45:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2843dea05948900cf66ccb77cfc4faf5c2684f5","tid":2329445,"uid":386778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T02:54:51.000Z","msg":"巴打搵吓自已學校有冇類似中大以下嘅service:<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.osa.cuhk.edu.hk/wacc/zh-TW/our-services/seeking-counselling\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.osa.cuhk.edu.hk%2Fwacc%2Fzh-TW%2Four-services%2Fseeking-counselling&d=%2B0Qob83dP4InFIGdpve28VQKcmgIyYy1b1J%2Bn%2Bjwg5M%3D&h=9a9d3fa8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www2.osa.cuhk.edu.hk/wacc/zh-TW/our-services/seeking-counselling</a><br />\n<br />\n另外，以下未必關事，但重點係早D嘗試搵唔同嘅求助方法，早D幫到自己：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ldy/showbiz/latest/20191122/1574395740219/【曾傳患腦瘤】李珊珊自爆患上驚恐症-曾徘徊瀕死邊緣\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u